; Regression test for issue #752: ArithmeticError: Adding amounts with different commodities: EUR != EUR (BZ#752)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/752
; This issue reported an ArithmeticError when adding EUR amounts from different sources.
; The bug appears to be fixed in current ledger.

P 2013/01/01 EUR $1.35

2013/01/01 Income
    Assets:EUR    500.00 EUR
    Income:Salary

2013/02/01 Income
    Assets:EUR    500.00 EUR
    Income:Salary

2013/03/01 Expense
    Expenses:Rent    300.00 EUR
    Assets:EUR

test bal
          700.00 EUR  Assets:EUR
          300.00 EUR  Expenses:Rent
        -1000.00 EUR  Income:Salary
--------------------
                   0
end test
